{
  "spec": {
    "title": "CSS Custom Highlight API Module Level 1",
    "url": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "to create a custom highlight",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#dom-highlight-highlight",
      "html": "When the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled idl-code has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"Highlight\" data-dfn-type=\"constructor\" data-export=\"\" data-lt=\"Highlight(...initialRanges)|constructor(...initialRanges)|Highlight()|constructor()\" id=\"dom-highlight-highlight\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><code>Highlight(AbstractRange... initialRanges)</code></dfn> constructor is invoked,\n\t\trun the following steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "Let <var>highlight</var> be the new <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#highlight\" id=\"ref-for-highlight③\">Highlight</a></code> object."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>highlight</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#dom-highlight-priority\" id=\"ref-for-dom-highlight-priority①\">priority</a></code> to <code>0</code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>highlight</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#dom-highlight-type\" id=\"ref-for-dom-highlight-type①\">type</a></code> to <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#dom-highlighttype-highlight\" id=\"ref-for-dom-highlighttype-highlight\">highlight</a></code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "For each <var>range</var> of <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#dom-highlight-highlight-initialranges-initialranges\" id=\"ref-for-dom-highlight-highlight-initialranges-initialranges\">initialRanges</a></code>,\n\t\t\t\tlet <var>rangeArg</var> be the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-convert-idl-to-javascript-value\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-convert-idl-to-javascript-value\">converting</a> <var>range</var> to an ECMAScript value,\n\t\t\t\tthen run <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#js-set-add\">the steps for a built-in setlike add function</a>,\n\t\t\t\twith <var>highlight</var> as the <code>this</code> value,\n\t\t\t\tand <var>rangeArg</var> as the argument."
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <var>highlight</var>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "to register a custom highlight",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#custom-highlight-name",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"custom-highlight-name\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">custom highlight name</dfn> assigned to a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#custom-highlight\" id=\"ref-for-custom-highlight⑧\">custom highlight</a> when it is <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#registered\" id=\"ref-for-registered④\">registered</a> is used to identify the highlight during styling (see <a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#styling-highlights\">§ 4 Styling Custom Highlights</a>).",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If any of the following are true, return the empty <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-sequence\" id=\"ref-for-idl-sequence⑥\">sequence</a>:</p>\n      <ul>\n       <li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>x</var> is negative</p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>y</var> is negative</p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>x</var> is greater than the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\">viewport</a> width excluding the size of a rendered scroll bar (if any)</p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>y</var> is greater than the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\">viewport</a> height excluding the size of a rendered scroll bar (if any)</p>\n      </li></ul>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise, return a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-sequence\" id=\"ref-for-idl-sequence⑦\">sequence</a> of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#custom-highlight\" id=\"ref-for-custom-highlight③⑨\">custom highlights</a> given by ordering the highlights contained in this <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#highlightregistry\" id=\"ref-for-highlightregistry④\">HighlightRegistry</a></code> in descending order of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-highlight-api-1/#priority\" id=\"ref-for-priority④\">priority</a>,\nincluding only those highlights that contain at least one <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#abstractrange\" id=\"ref-for-abstractrange④\">AbstractRange</a></code> <var>abstractRange</var> that satisfies the following:</p>\n      <ul>\n       <li data-md=\"\">\n        <p>Let <var>range</var> be a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#range\" id=\"ref-for-range⑨\">Range</a></code> object whose <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-range-start-node\" id=\"ref-for-concept-range-start-node①\">start node</a> and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-range-end-node\" id=\"ref-for-concept-range-end-node①\">end node</a> are set to <var>abstractRange</var>’s <span id=\"ref-for-concept-range-start-node②\">start node</span> and <span id=\"ref-for-concept-range-end-node②\">end node</span> respectively,\nand <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-range-start-offset\" id=\"ref-for-concept-range-start-offset\">start offset</a> and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-range-end-offset\" id=\"ref-for-concept-range-end-offset\">end offset</a> are set to <var>abstractRange</var>’s <span id=\"ref-for-concept-range-start-offset①\">start offset</span> and <span id=\"ref-for-concept-range-end-offset①\">end offset</span> respectively.</p>\n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p>The coordinates <var>x</var>,<var>y</var> fall inside at least one of the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.fxtf.org/geometry-1/#domrect\" id=\"ref-for-domrect\">DOMRect</a></code>s returned by calling <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view-1/#dom-range-getclientrects\" id=\"ref-for-dom-range-getclientrects\">getClientRects()</a></code> on <var>range</var>.</p>\n        \n       </li><li data-md=\"\">\n        <p>The <var>range</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-range-commonancestorcontainer\" id=\"ref-for-dom-range-commonancestorcontainer\">commonAncestorContainer</a></code> is not in a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-shadow-tree\" id=\"ref-for-concept-shadow-tree②\">shadow tree</a> or is in a <span id=\"ref-for-concept-shadow-tree③\">shadow tree</span> whose <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-element-shadow-root\" id=\"ref-for-concept-element-shadow-root\">shadow root</a> is <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-contain\" id=\"ref-for-list-contain\">contained by</a> by <var>options</var>.<var>shadowRoots</var>.</p>\n      </li></ul>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}